How To Handle DropDowns?
dropdown = page.locator("#fruits")
Get All <option> Elements
options = dropdown.locator("option")
print("Total options:", options.count())
options.count() ‚Üí number of <option> elements.
Use .nth(index) to access each option.
for i in range(options.count()):
    print(options.nth(i).inner_text())

